description:
The Road to Salvation, Part 2 of 4

A rescue mission goes wrong when our heroes encounter Neo Zombies in the forest. But they also pick up a stray in the form of "Princess Aimee," who happens to look exactly like Jamie! Could this be a Salvation trick? Sorcery shenanigans? An obvious, but hard to accept truth?
name: The Road to Salvation, Part 2 of 4

volume.name: Chaos Campus: Sorority Girls Vs. Zombies

description: Comic Shop News is comics' weekly newsletter. Each issue is full-color, 8-12 pages in length, and features CSNsider, news, and interviews. CSN has a complete monthly checklist (complete with PREVIEWS item codes), plus exclusive CSN Hot Picks, 'Fab Firsts,' and a monthly checklist of all the first issues for the month!
As the mechanical gods take a look into Cheetah’s past to find the truth, we take a look into Cheetah’s horrifying adolescence.
name: Big Cats Part 2 of 3

description:
No Childish Games, part 1

The city is brought down by a tide of child abductions. Kids disappear in groups. Danila and Sneak are pretty sure that there are demonic forces involved...
name: No Childish Games Part 1

description:
Black Sun

The quaint American desert town of Mistletoe and its people are on the brink of economic and spiritual collapse. That is, until a passing stranger presents them with an opportunity for salvation or something far more unfathomable.
name: Black Sun

description:
Sold Relic, part 5

Travelling through time, young man Andrey Radov has to collect magical gems and retrieve his family's cross to return to his era and stop the evil Magister of a secret order!

It's 1877 and the third siege of Plevna during the Russo-Turkish war. In Russian camp Andrey meets the "White General" Skobelev and his aide - Igor, Andrey's brother! Having resigned himself to his fate, the newly-born friar begins to prepare for the upcoming battle... And there is something to prepare for: Turkish general Osman Pasha intends to win the battle, calling upon the underworld forces and resorting to the help of the Magister! But Andrey manages to break their insidious plan and successfully retrieves the first Power Gem - the Ruby of Shakhriman!

Meanwhile, enraged by the failure, the Magister is trying to deal with Andrey another way: he sneaks into the hospital and turns off the poor guy's life-support machine...
name: Sold Relic Part 5

description:
Plague Doctor, part 5

Major Grom is getting closer to solving the mystery of The Plague Doctor. While walking Yulia home after a date he notices "London City" mall in flames and realizes that another keyword murder is being committed there! Grom rushes to the building to find businessman Bekhtiev crucified on the scaffolding of his own mall! And right beside him is standing... The Plague Doctor himself!
name: Plague Doctor Part 5

description: Now with 50% more indie awesomeness! Make mine INDIE presents information and preview pages from some of the best indie comics around!

Eye to Eye

A month has passed since TrenchMouth ravaged Chicago. Peace has reigned until Doctor Anarchy wreaks havoc. All of this and more as Titan meets the mysterious Mantis. Is he friend or the worst kind of foe?

Note: The digital edition (9/21/2016) for this issue was released before the print edition.
name: Eye to Eye

description: Nexus has finally escaped the Netherzone and returned home, only to realize the same fate that befell Osceola is destined for Ylum! Gourmando the World-Eater is on his way!

Captured and imprisoned by the Strategic Defense Initiative, Matthew Baker, is scared and being pushed to the edge of sanity. Alone and separated from the father who loves him how far can he be pushed until he cracks and decides to push back? This issue is sure to pull on the heartstrings and make you ask yourself, “ Does protecting the interests of any country justify dehumanizing an innocent child?”

Just when you thought you were safe! Rock and Roll Biographies are breaking new ground and going punk for an issue! Featuring the Bay Areas one and only true punksters NOFX! See how Fat Mike formed the seminal hardcore punk group and how they achieved success with no support from the world!
name: Vol. 2

description: Occult investigator Alice Creed has paid the price for using necromancy time and again, but in a world forever unleashing horrors beyond comprehension, Alice's spiritual debt continues to mount. This collector's edition of the hit Dark Horse Presents series includes both of Alex de Campi (Grindhouse) and Jerry Ordway's (Planetary/ JLA: Terra Occulta) original Semiautomagic arcs, as well as three brand-new stories! Alice confronts a college student possessed by a demonic video game, an army of evil mannequins, the most horrific inflight entertainment ever, nightmarish versions of children's fantasy creatures, and Hollywood occultists using the dark arts for more than preserving their looks. Guest artist Lara Margarida (Flash Gordon) joins de Campi for a tale of a manic pixie dream girl's disillusionment, revealing the secret history of Alice's unstuck-in-time friend Harriet. These five tales reach deep into the terrifying void beyond the routine horror of myth and legend, a void all too familiar to Alice Creed.

volume.name: Semiautomagic: The Bomb that Will Bring Us Together/Childhood's End Collector's Edition

description:
Supernatural bounty hunter John Tower has long been a man shrouded in mystery. Now, discover what set him on this path of horror as his origins are finally uncovered, revealing just what Tower is risking his life to find!

While Tower and his allies infiltrate the Brotherhood's fortress for the last artifact, the Brotherhood gets wind of their trespassing and mobilizes against them.

The Heart of the Matter

After the catastrophic destruction of the wellspring in the last issue, Zoe lies in a bizarre, unbreakable sleep while the deadly Withering Man draws ever closer. But within this mystical sleep, secrets are revealed and the origin of evil is told.
name: The Heart of the Matter

description: When the Mothman, Bigfoot, and crew come knocking on Solomon Kane’s door, Kane realizes no holds are barred in this final battle. The team is divided in two while some disperse to free the other creatures of folklore and some head into what will be their final fight with Kane himself. Surrounded by destruction a guest appearance from a famous urban legend may be just what the team needs to survive.

Hanafuda tells the supernatural tale of Izuna, a noble turned demon hunter, travelling across Japan to slay the oni that stole the life of his beloved Lady Kiri. Izuna encounters a young fox that possesses the ability to shapeshift and the duo journey together to exact revenge on the oni. Hanafuda, or "flower cards", is a Japanese card game where each suit of cards represents a month and flower. Like the game, each chapter in Hanafuda corresponds to a different suit.
name: Vol. 1

description: This massive, official hardcover art book was only available for a short time with the release of BioShock 2, and is quite sought-after now. Containing 168 pages of gorgeous, full-color artwork from the game, fans will be delighted to find stunning concept paintings, detailed character and weapon designs, storyboards, a gallery of posters, and much more in this exhaustive volume. Accompanying the images are insights from the artists and developers themselves as they explain some of the lore behind the characters and what went into bringing this unique world to life. This is a must-have book for any fan of the games or of art deco art in general.
name: HC

volume.name: Deco Devolution: The Art of BioShock 2

deck: Alpha Flight battles some random villains, but ultimately narrowly defeats Omega Flight after a horrific turn of events.  The Hulk makes an appearance but fails to defeat Canada's premier super team.  Finally, Secret Wars II crosses into our story but fails to derails it.
description:
Canada's mightiest heroes face threats of all sizes, ranging from the overweight Pink Pearl to the Maniacal alchemist Diablo! And when the terrible secret of Sasquatch's origin is revealed, Alpha Flight must battle the Great Beasts in their own realm - and pay a fearsome price! Then, Alpha Flight's former leader, Guardian, returns from the grave - or does he? What's he doing palling around with the villainous Omega Flight? And where does the Beyonder fit in? Finally, when Alpha Flight goes fishing in another dimension, they accidentally hook the Incredible Hulk! Will the jade giant smash the heroes beyond all repair? Only the series new creative team knows! It's north-of-the-border action just the way you like it!

Collects Alpha Flight #20-29, Incredible Hulk #313 & Secret Wars II #4.
name: Volume Three

description:
Receive the gift of laughter - The Dandy Annual! It's the ultimate festive treat - better tasting than sweet mince pies, funnier than a box full of Christmas cracker jokes... and not a sprout in sight!

It may be cold outside, but inside it's warm and full of funny adventures with Desperate Dan, Winker Watson, plus comic stars Korky the Cat and the Smasher!

Give your laughter muscles the treat they crave - The Dandy Annual!

name: Die Ungeheuer vom Dach der Welt
